step.reason:
\text{Generally speaking, a line L whose} \\
\text{equation is }
\dfrac{x-x_1}{a}=\dfrac{y-y_1}{b}=\dfrac{z-z_1}{c}, \\
\text{whose directions ratios a,b and c, would equal} \\
\text{any other line with the same direction ratios.}

